    (Translated by Google) We went to the star hotel in Tangier in August 2017.
    More or less positive points:
    * the restaurant which offers several varieties, but that's not what is lacking in Tangier!
    * the kindness and reliability of the staff.
    Negative points :
    We found a lot of discomfort there:
    Lots of noise and whistling wind through very poor quality aluminum windows;
    The hotel is located on a very busy main road (6 lane road) through which all types of traffic passes including heavy goods vehicles. In short, it is not possible to sleep or even find a moment of calm during the day;
    The kitchen not practical;
    Sleeping bathroom (flush flowing all the time),
    Very beldis furniture;
    Old-fashioned television and no interesting channels;
    Small swimming pool and located on the terrace with a very strong wind that makes a strong whirlpool and prevents you from staying there more than a few minutes. (not possible to sunbathe in view of the strong wind);
    View of the popular districts through the terrace (and swimming pool);
    The price is not given at all. you can stay in one of the hotels or residences right by the beach for the same price!
    When you go out at night, you risk wasting an hour in traffic jams between the hotel and the tourist area.
    In short: A very tiring and unbearable stay.

    Le prix n'est pas du tout donn. on peut sjourner dans l'un des htels ou rsidences juste ct de la plage avec le mme prix !
    Quand vous sortez le soir, vous risquez de perdre une heure dans les embouteillages entre l'htel et la zone touristique.
    Bref : Sjour vraiment trs fatigant et insoutenable.

    About this hotel

    On a busy commercial street, this casual hotel is 3 km from Municipal Beach, 5 km from Kasbah Museum and 13 km from Tangier Ibn Battouta Airport.

    The relaxed, airy rooms feature living areas with sofas, plus Wi-Fi and TVs. Apartments add 1, 2 or 4 bedrooms, as well as living rooms and kitchens.

    Amenities include an informal restaurant with a glass-enclosed terrace, in addition to a rooftop pool. Parking is also available.

    Check-in time: 2:00 PM
    Check-out time: 11:00 AM
